RESOLUTION

HP recommends the following mitigation steps to reduce the risk of this
vulnerability for HP StoreEver ESL E-series Tape Library and HP Virtual
Library System (VLS).

  HP StoreEver ESL E-series Tape Library

    - Disable DHCP and only use static IP addressing.

  HP Virtual Library System (VLS)

    - Disable DHCP and only use static IP addressing.
    - If using version 6.X firmware, contact HP support to have Apache
disabled on the product

